  <summary date="2020-12-11T16:19:48Z" status="Passed House">Timely Review of Infrastructure Act 

This bill authorizes the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC)to address insufficient compensation of its personnel without regard to civil service laws.FERC must consult with the Office of Personnel Management when making a determination of the appropriate compensation for its personnel.</summary>
